        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8 text-gray-300">
          AI-powered solutions for retail businesses that want to improve customer service, streamline operations, and increase profitability.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-accent text-lg px-8 py-4">
            Get Free Assessment
          </a>
          <a href="#use-cases" class="btn btn-secondary text-lg px-8 py-4">
